  "subject": "Convert filter-types.properties to an INI file",
  "commit_message": "Convert filter-types.properties to an INI file\n\nUse Commons Configuration2 to parse the existing properties file using\nthe INI parser. This allows the instance-group-types filter list to be specified on\nseparate lines (instead of comma-separated).\n\nIt also allows for additional INI sections to be specified (in a future\nchange), so that TOSCA to Java mappings can also be stored in this file.\n\nChange-Id: I186ae7785443e2928c4394181a2b3fc58ac2268b\nIssue-ID: AAI-2121\nSigned-off-by: mark.j.leonard <mark.j.leonard@gmail.com>\n",
